  "text": "Five major pathogens Escherichia coli, Clostridium perfringens, Campylobacter jejuni, Salmonella enterica and Bacillus cereus were confirmed by SSCP using 16S rRNA gene [CITATION_1] . In our previous studies we have developed the species-specific DNA fingerprints for species identification and diagnosis of phytobacterium pathogens and their diseases .",
